40fdca791d2.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-82e677544ab9f0cf.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-7bbe11e50038bf9a.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/517-a1df7b2d5b4618d3.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-bfd28e850380ad24.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/173-070ddf095c6be93e.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/274-f03681e9fcaf2d52.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-4e6b976042042964.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/970-5a94b8b7d39da710.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/products/%5Bslug%5D/page-b37b28506992a909.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://cdn.snipcart.com\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"/><title>Hand-Crocheted Rainbow Wavy Bucket Hat | The Wookporium | Wookporium</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Stand out in the crowd with a premium, hand-crocheted ruffled bucket hat in a vibrant rainbow pattern. Pure artisan festival fashion built for the music.\"/><meta name=\"author\" content=\"Wookporium\"/><link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/manifest.json\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"festival fashion,handmade clothing,festival jewelry,crochet apparel,natural jewelry,sustainable fashion,bohemian clothing,rave wear,festival accessories,handcrafted jewelry\"/><meta name=\"creator\" content=\"Wookporium\"/><meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\"/><meta name=\"googlebot\" content=\"index, follow, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-snippet:-1\"/><meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\"/><meta name=\"google-site-verification\" content=\"your-google-verification-code\"/><meta name=\"mobile-web-app-capable\" content=\"yes\"/><meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-title\" content=\"Wookporium\"/><meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style\" content=\"default\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Wavy Hat\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Bring the ultimate burst of color to the crowd with our signature Wavy Bucket Hat. Hand-crocheted using a stunning kaleidoscope pattern of ultra-vibrant, high-contrast rainbow shades, this piece features a perfectly flared, ruffled brim designed for maximum movement and effortless festival style.\n\nMeticulously stitched from an incredibly soft, breathable yarn blend, it provides comfort all day and into the night. It is lightweight enough to stay comfortable during high-energy dance sets and durable enough to handle packing, travel, and the dust of the festival grounds. Each piece is crafted entirely by hand with absolute love and precision—no two are completely identical, ensuring your festival look remains entirely unique.\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/7iiji3rf/production/03dfda96020c826659c06b91cedfcbeb8056dbc8-3456x4561.jpg\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"Wavy Hat\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Wavy Hat\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Bring the ultimate burst of color to the crowd with our signature Wavy Bucket Hat. Hand-crocheted using a stunning kaleidoscope pattern of ultra-vibrant, high-contrast rainbow shades, this piece features a perfectly flared, ruffled brim designed for maximum movement and effortless festival style.\n\nMeticulously stitched from an incredibly soft, breathable yarn blend, it provides comfort all day and into the night. It is lightweight enough to stay comfortable during high-energy dance sets and durable enough to handle packing, travel, and the dust of the festival grounds. Each piece is cr