ion%2Fb8a409760342dcc75cbefb6e7b7d8e7e81bdbd06-3456x4561.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2F7iiji3rf%2Fproduction%2Fb8a409760342dcc75cbefb6e7b7d8e7e81bdbd06-3456x4561.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></button></div><p class=\"text-sm text-secondary text-center\">Click thumbnails to view different images</p></div></div><div class=\"glass-light glass-shadow rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"px-4 py-1 bg-white/50 text-secondary uppercase text-sm font-semibold rounded-full border border-white/20\">headwear</span><span class=\"px-4 py-1 bg-accent/90 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full shadow-sm\">One of a Kind ✨</span></div><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-header font-bold text-dark-brown drop-shadow-sm\">Wavy Hat</h1><div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-4 border-b border-brown-warm/10 pb-6\"><span class=\"text-5xl font-bold text-primary drop-shadow-sm\">$<!-- -->74.00</span><span class=\"text-2xl text-secondary line-through opacity-70\">$<!-- -->100.00</span></div><div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\"><p class=\"text-dark-brown leading-relaxed\">Bring the ultimate burst of color to the crowd with our signature Wavy Bucket Hat. Hand-crocheted using a stunning kaleidoscope pattern of ultra-vibrant, high-contrast rainbow shades, this piece features a perfectly flared, ruffled brim designed for maximum movement and effortless festival style.\n\nMeticulously stitched from an incredibly soft, breathable yarn blend, it provides comfort all day and into the night. It is lightweight enough to stay comfortable during high-energy dance sets and durable enough to handle packing, travel, and the dust of the festival grounds. Each piece is crafted entirely by hand with absolute love and precision—no two are completely identical, ensuring your festival look remains entirely unique.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-dark-brown mb-2\">Materials:</h3><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-white/50 border border-white/20 text-secondary text-sm rounded-full\">recycled yard</span></div></div><div class=\"bg-white/40 p-4 rounded-lg border border-white/20\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-dark-brown mb-2\">Care Instructions:</h3><p class=\"text-secondary text-sm\">Care: Hand wash cold, lay flat to dry</p></div><p class=\"text-accent font-semibold animate-pulse\">Only <!-- -->1<!-- --> left in stock!</p><div class=\"pt-4\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><button class=\"\n          snipcart-add-item w-full py-4 px-8 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg\n          transition-all duration-200 focus-visible-ring\n          bg-primary text-white hover:bg-primary-dark active:scale-95 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl\n        \" data-item-id=\"wavy-hat\" data-item-price=\"74.00\" data-item-name=\"Wavy Hat\" data-item-description=\"Bring the ultimate burst of color to the crowd with our signature Wavy Bucket Hat. Hand-crocheted using a stunning kaleidoscope pattern of ultra-vibrant, high-contrast rainbow shades, this piece features a perfectly flared, ruffled brim designed for maximum movement and effortless festival style.\n\nMeticulously stitched from an incredibly soft, breathable yarn blend, it provides comfort all day and into the night. It is lightweight enough to stay comfortable during high-energy dance sets and durable enough to handle packing, travel, and the dust of the festival grounds. Each piece is crafted entirely by hand with absolute love and precision—no two are completely identical, ensuring your festival look remains entirely unique.\" data-item-image=\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/7iiji3rf/production/03dfda96020c826659c06b91cedfcbeb8056dbc8-3456x4561.jpg\" data-item-url=\"/products/wavy-hat\" data-item-categories=\"headwear\" data-item-weight=\"10\" data-item-quantity=\"1\" data-item-max-quantity=\"1\" aria-label=\"Add Wavy Hat to cart\"><span class=\"mr-2\">🛒</span>Add to Cart - $<!-- -->74.00</button><p 